ceive email updates close patriot gold corp clarification and retraction of previously issued historical disclosure  patriot gold   stock symbol pgol   receive email updates submit home about patriot news investors projects contact company news tweet company news patriot gold corp clarification and retraction of previously issued historical disclosureoctober   las vegas nevada  patriot gold corp patriot or the company otcqbpgol announces that as a result of a review by the british columbia securities commission bcsc the company is issuing this news release to retract certain historical disclosure pertaining to the bruner property which as previously filed in press releases and posted on the companys website was not compliant with national instrument   standards of disclosure for mineral projects ni  bruner property on may   and september   the company issued press releases in which a historical resource estimate pertaining to the bruner property did not comply with ni  as the company did not disclose the source and date of such statement the relevance and reliability of the historical estimate the key assumptions parameters and methods used to prepare the historical estimate an explanation of the differences between the category of resource stated and current accepted categories of mineral resources and disclosure on what work needs to be done to upgrade or verify the historical estimate as a current mineral reserve or mineral resource all as required by section  of ni  after further review of the source information the company is unable to restate the estimate in compliance with ni  requirements consequently the company retracts the estimate described herein in its entirety the company advises and cautions readers that the retracted disclosure may continue to be found in the public domain robert coale is the qualified person as defined by ni  who has reviewed and approved the technical information in this news release as it relates to the bruner property disclaimer