tnering with us we welcome you to contact us     patriot gold corp all rights reserved   terms of use home about patriot news investors projects contact projects  patriot gold   stock symbol pgol   receive email updates submit home about patriot news investors projects contact overview moss mine bruner gold project vernal gold project overview patriot gold corp is focused on developing its arizona and nevada precious metals projects and assets we have a royalty interest in the moss mine a substantial arizonabased gold and silver project which is now moving towards commercial production we also have a royalty interest in the bruner gold project which although not yet in production has delivered impressive assays an updated resource and a preliminary economic assessment our vernal gold and windy peak projects are still in their early stages the moss mine is located within arizonas oatman district which has produced around  million ounces of gold historically the bruner and vernal gold projects are both located within nevadas walker lane which hosts numerous major deposits including the goldfield over  million ounces of post production and present reserves and the comstock over  million ounces moss mine bruner gold project vernal gold project     patriot gold corp all rights reserved   terms of use home about patriot news investors projects contact pgol stock price  patriot gold corp stock quote us otc  marketwatch sections watchlist signup • login search bulletin us europe asia fx rates futures range d d m m m y y dow    sp     nasdaq    globaldow    gold    oil    sp  movers ctas  cof  etfc  syf  hp  isrg  hban  chk  latest newsall times eastern a us stocks poised for soft start after imf cuts growth forecast a polish zloty rises as polands president plans veto for judicial revamp a opinion bipartisan political squabbling over drug prices has already cost biotech companies  billion a opinion investing according to your values can also make you money a opinion here’s 